name: USDTZ
description: The USDT BEP-20 Smart Contract represents the Tether (USDT) stablecoin on the Binance Smart Chain (BSC), adhering to the BEP-20 token standard. This smart contract ensures that USDT transactions are fast, secure, and cost-efficient, leveraging the speed and low fees of Binance Smart Chain while maintaining the price stability pegged to the US Dollar
